Dear all,

The IIT Madras Chess club in association with ChessBase India is proud to
present the Institute Rapid Chess Championship on Saturday, 29 October.

*Prizes for the winners: (Sponsored by institute gymkhana and ChessBase)*

*I - Gold Medal and 2 Volume Instructional DVD by Vishwanathan Anand worth
Rs 1799/- along with a poster of Vishy Anand*

*II - Silver Medal with ChessBase premium account for 6 months worth Rs
750/-*

*III - Bronze Medal with ChessBase premium account for 3 months worth Rs
375/-*

*Venue: 3rd floor, Gymkhana*
*Reporting time: 10 AM*

Those interested, please fill this form
<https://goo.gl/forms/Whf7RgMt9dZQhsKz1>.

About ChessBase: ChessBase is the world's leading seller of chess software,
databases, gadgets and other products which are used by tournament Chess
players all over the world right from amateurs to World Champions.
ChessBase India was founded recently by International Master Sagar Shah to
help Indian players to access their products easily.

